briefdescription.para: initializes startup SOC-related values like lookup from nonvolatile ram at startup
sets SOC value with a parameter between 0.0 and 100.0.
initializes the SOC values with lookup table (mean, min and max).
integrates current over time to calculate SOC.
initializes the area for SOF (where derating starts and is fully active).

detaileddescription.para: Pseudocode for linear function parameter extraction with 2 points slope = (y2 - y1) / (x2-x1) offset = y1 - (slope) * x1 function y= slope * x + offset
Calculation made with the function SOF_Calculate().

briefdescription.para: Header for SOX module, responsible for calculation of current derating and of SOC.
